što će isplivati na površinu.

00:39:31.992 --> 00:39:34.286
Jesi li dobro?

00:39:34.370 --> 00:39:36.288
Tiha si.

00:39:37.331 --> 00:39:39.291
Jesam.

00:39:40.334 --> 00:39:43.337
Posao?

00:39:43.420 --> 00:39:45.381
Što se danas dogodilo?

00:39:49.510 --> 00:39:53.180
